					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">Espozo wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">One thing I've always wondered: Why didn't Mario Paint use 8bpp mode?</div><br />Not enough memory to hold both the background and animation layers in memory, plus the undo buffer and everything else. Besides, there are no modes with two 8bpp layers, so the animation layer has to be 4bpp.</div>

